{
  "texts": [
    "The RNA portion of the SNARE-seq2 (snare) dataset from Bakken et al.",
    "46 and Plongthongkum et al.",
    "50 was used in this section.",
    "First, the snare data was subsetted to the DART-FISH genes.",
    "Then, DART-FISH and snare data were both normalized (scanpy.pp.normalize_total(., target_sum = 1000)) followed by lognormalization (scanpy.pp.log1p(.))."
  ]
}